                <supplied reason="lost">I</supplied>ulius a ratio<lb break="no" n="2"/>ne tegularia An<lb break="no" n="3"/>thimus cum cen<lb break="no" n="4"/>sum par<surplus>i</surplus>avit <lb n="5"/>DXXXIII <lb n="6"/>ago gratias <lb n="7"/>domine </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Solve quod mi<lb break="no" n="2"/>nus fecisti et <lb n="3"/>sic gratias a<lb break="no" n="4"/>ge et duas <lb n="5"/>amplius quia min<lb break="no" n="6"/>us numerasti
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ziegel in 3 Fragmente gebrochen. 2 gegenständig angeordnete, jeweils an den Schmalseiten des Ziegels beginnende eingeritzte Inschriften. (B): AE 1979: Z. 2/3: Ant/himus; AE 1979, Pereira Menault: Z. 3/4: censum pariavit; CIL II² 14, 35 b: Z. 12/13: min/nus.</p>
            </div>
